{
  "html": "<h3 id=\"installation-1\">Installation</h3>\n\n<p>Install the SDK via Rubygems by adding it to your <code class=\"highlighter-rouge\">Gemfile</code>:</p>\n\n<pre class=\"highlight\"><code><span class=\"n\">gem</span> <span class=\"s2\">\"sentry-raven\"</span>\n</code></pre>\n\n<h3 id=\"configuration-1\">Configuration</h3>\n\n<p>Add <code class=\"highlighter-rouge\">use Raven::Rack</code> to your <code class=\"highlighter-rouge\">config.ru</code> or other rackup file (this is automatically inserted in Rails):</p>\n\n<pre class=\"highlight\"><code><span class=\"nb\">require</span> <span class=\"s1\">'raven'</span>\n\n<span class=\"no\">Raven</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"nf\">configure</span> <span class=\"k\">do</span> <span class=\"o\">|</span><span class=\"n\">config</span><span class=\"o\">|</span>\n  <span class=\"n\">config</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"nf\">dsn</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"s1\">'___DSN___'</span>\n<span class=\"k\">end</span>\n\n<span class=\"n\">use</span> <span class=\"no\">Raven</span><span class=\"o\">::</span><span class=\"no\">Rack</span>\n</code></pre>\n<!-- TODO-ADD-VERIFICATION-EXAMPLE -->", 
  "link": "https://docs.sentry.io/clients/ruby/integrations/rack/", 
  "id": "ruby-rack", 
  "name": "Rack"
}
